s that anyone from my nation who dies without associating partners with Allah will eventually enter Paradise.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37917,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/al-mawjibatan\/","url_meta":{"origin":33258,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: Two inescapable consequences in Afterlife","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Khuraym ibn Fatik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are two inevitabilities: The one who declares there is no God but Allah, or who is a believer in Allah, will enter Paradise, and the one who dies while associating partners with Allah will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33296,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/28\/whoever-dies-dua-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33258,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Whoever dies calling upon a partner with Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, made a statement and I made another in his presence. The Prophet said, \u201cWhoever dies while calling upon a partner besides Allah will enter the Hellfire.\u201d I said, \u201cWhoever dies without calling upon a partner besides Allah will\u